# Tailwind Conventions

- Use design tokens from tailwind.config (colors, radius, shadows) instead of arbitrary values where tokens exist
- Prefer semantic tokens: `bg-primary`, `text-muted-foreground` over raw hex
- Use `cn()` from lib/utils for conditional class merging
- Avoid inline arbitrary values like `w-[677px]` when a token or standard utility exists
